    "id": "overview"
  }, "Overview"), mdx("p", null, "Webizen Pro is an initiative that is centred upon the production of advanced hardware/software solutions for specialist and luxury markets.\xA0\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "The initiatives hardware stack is intended to be deployed in various form-factors; including, as a tower-like workstation and/or rack-mountable platform (AC or DC powered).\xA0"), mdx("p", null, "Webizen and Webizen Pro platforms are a hardware & software solution; providing a new operating system built on top of linux.\xA0 This platform provides APIs to rapidly produce software on webizen systems using web-based languages.\xA0"), mdx("h3", {
